name: Shinshu Inu
description: Shinshu Inu ($SHINSHU) is a community-focused, decentralized cryptocurrency with instant rewards for its holders. Shinshu Inu aims to become the leader in P2P mobile payments within the crypto space. Shinshu Inu offers a seamless way to send payments to friends and family via a mobile app. Forms of payment will be vetted tokens within the Shinshu Inu ecosystem.
